gdwyAOLY5benEC39JDHm8cN0rZL2.Name: Helena
gdwyAOLY5benEC39JDHm8cN0rZL2.SelfIntro:
I'm someone that has been fairly successful in life all alone, but realize to unlock true happiness... I need a partner in crime to share adventures, a muse to inspire greater ambitions and a best friend to love and support and be loved and supported by.
At my core, I'm all about multifaceted uniqueness - a wide range of contrasting, even dueling traits and textures all in perfect balance make me who I am. 
I'm a funny, loud shit talker that loves conversation, but I'm also a deep thinker that loves to appreciate beauty and reflect in silence.  I'm a man's man that enjoys the violence and aggression of football (go Niners!), boxing, UFC, shooting guns and working on/ driving loud, fast cars, but I'm also a passionate, artistic romantic that enjoys musicals, the opera, museums and romantic comedies. I love wild crazy nights dancing to hip hop and house while drinking Fernet and Scotch, but I also love staying in an entire weekend to cook and binge on Netflix and video games.
I'm definitely here to find someone special and would ultimately like to find a serious relationship, but that does not mean the journey there has to be serious... I am chill enough to know something worthwhile takes time, so I always try to go with the flow while laughing and smiling as much as possible along the way.
